{"tid":951970,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"找不到的網絡神曲，8、90後我們的回憶","createTime":"2018-12-22T17:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T16:17:15.000Z","uid":19592,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c1e7065c9286d36b270836a6da21bc1182340419","tid":951970,"uid":19592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T17:35:39.000Z","msg":"我真係好想搵返哩兩首歌，跪求巴絲們分享。<br />\n1.《他朝會更好》<br />\n由一名不知名男子所創作，<br />\n在短短一分鐘內，重覆他朝會更好這句歌詞，<br />\n再不斷升key，令觀眾深深記入腦海，<br />\n並感受到歌手心中對明天的期盼。<br />\n暗合當年「聽日一定會好天嘅」廣告的心態，<br />\n成為不少人每天必聽的歌曲。<br />\n<br />\n對後世的影響深遠，《原來他不夠愛我》以及《經過一些秋與冬》等歌曲，當中把曲名和副歌重覆，以達至一眾mk可以成功用一句說話叫春，紅爆全城，便是以此作爲參考。<br />\n<br />\nP.S.在youtube能找到的那段西裝友合唱版，只是這歌的cover，原創者的單人版本感染力極為豐富，後世所有cover都無法達到該水準。<br />\n<br />\n2.《我唔識拍拖》（好似係）<br />\n由第一代網絡紅人Ruby主唱，保留Twins的走音合唱原則，再加上劃時代的嘻哈段落，領先樂壇一大步。<br />\n曲中清楚描寫一班年輕男女對戀愛的失望，一句我唔識拍拖，分開好過（好似係）令無數mk仔mk妹重回單身，思考自身價值。<br />\n間接引申出後世的所有交友app，分開是新的開始，懂拍拖我們嘗試只做愛，這種浪漫的後現代新愛情觀念。"},{"pid":"0ec545255ffc53e377b046b7c549948f30778cbc","tid":951970,"uid":19592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T17:42:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a58313ab6e52dbc0c55ae08576abe5416ee3600e","tid":951970,"uid":19592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T17:45:22.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"d271139b3a6f2f7536604fa3f6edf8f895f1df7e","tid":951970,"uid":19592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T17:45:36.000Z","msg":"係咪已經冇人聽過"},{"pid":"c5426be061bbd0cd712f8ee41fc6daf835f2fe48","tid":951970,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T17:47:32.000Z","msg":"我唔識拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce894c9d66f9c2bb519b21844341ec48d0427ed5","tid":951970,"uid":19592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5426be061bbd0cd712f8ee41fc6daf835f2fe48","tid":951970,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T17:47:32.000Z","msg":"我唔識拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T18:00:24.000Z","msg":"巴打有冇聽過"},{"pid":"dddefbed3c688b4250990433fa23fae63e641f61","tid":951970,"uid":20492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T18:02:14.000Z","msg":"臨別擁抱"},{"pid":"67174bcaa605d1fe7add044d914100d72eb7c932","tid":951970,"uid":19592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dddefbed3c688b4250990433fa23fae63e641f61","tid":951970,"uid":20492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T18:02:14.000Z","msg":"臨別擁抱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T18:05:38.000Z","msg":"我決定開過個新post"},{"pid":"562f7203bbef18d635e78feef52c1b76707e6d2c","tid":951970,"uid":161190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T18:11:43.000Z","msg":"當你孤單你會想起誰<br />\n<br />\n而家聽好有感觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc562e7c267a25723b37e3afb46a802c3a495b1","tid":951970,"uid":1585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T18:20:35.000Z","msg":"寵愛，虛擬幻想,趕你走"},{"pid":"1428e040d409f0e202afc7d09b8786de1f4ca7aa","tid":951970,"uid":13467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T18:24:24.000Z","msg":"記得佢唱他朝會更好唱到冇氣"},{"pid":"7c40cb63457057dd36b5d35f9642701056075fb2","tid":951970,"uid":19592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1428e040d409f0e202afc7d09b8786de1f4ca7aa","tid":951970,"uid":13467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T18:24:24.000Z","msg":"記得佢唱他朝會更好唱到冇氣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T18:35:14.000Z","msg":"太好聽了 再也回不去"},{"pid":"54597463c6993c72efe478fd352a50aeb4fdf5d7","tid":951970,"uid":112719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:15:41.000Z","msg":"推，有冇人有backup"},{"pid":"9bccfbde53121c87365219a7561d90a10304be0b","tid":951970,"uid":19592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54597463c6993c72efe478fd352